{"tid":959114,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【無妄之災！倒楣車遭放飛劍　頭冚慘留刮痕】","createTime":"2018-12-28T10:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T14:01:43.000Z","uid":225464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0e6da61ccbd78401895e2e54c8af09d2217fd0","tid":959114,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181228/bkn-20181228170300393-1228_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181228%2Fbkn-20181228170300393-1228_00822_001.html&d=JSnEAddLjxlMXR%2BXYQ2aFP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6ccde154\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181228/bkn-20181228170300393-1228_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z1LoYeS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1LoYeS.jpg&h=047494b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>無妄之災！倒楣車遭放飛劍　頭冚慘留刮痕</strong><br />\n<br />\n私家車泊在街旁，竟亦招惹無妄之災？近日元朗有車輛遭人亂吐口水，車頭更離奇出現刮痕，到底發生甚麼事？<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook群組「PLAY HARD 玩硬」的影片所見，周四（27日）晚上11時許，有私家車停泊在元朗水車館街，一名紅衣少年手持手機，突然從路旁走向車頭，五指合成爪狀，在車頭蓋上掃了一下。<br />\n<br />\n他低頭查看一會後，便轉身離去。未幾少年又再折返，向私家車作出疑似吐口水的姿態，再向前方的貨Van故技重施，始施施然離去。<br />\n<br />\n受害私家車車主怒斥︰「你吐我架車口水做乜X嘢呢？如果我泊得衰，你咪報警拖我車囉！你係咪覺得自己好X型？」又指已就事件報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n不少網友留言大鬧少年：「佢係咪痴線㗎」、「聽晚捕佢啦」，但有人指車主或有錯在先：「首先要舉報自己違例泊車」。"},{"pid":"61267a50a6485a0db9225adbe6cfc0a13f2a7687","tid":959114,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e8fa181b7fd5d07a8cf20e240d49880ac093510","tid":959114,"uid":75072,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"違泊就要俾你搞 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  On9網民"},{"pid":"103a12c1d0e490f7564cd8bcb79afd06c774e2c6","tid":959114,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆